name: Flying Farting Ducks 'n EGGs by Karrie Ross

metadata.name: Flying Farting Ducks 'n EGGs by Karrie Ross
metadata.description:
Flying Farting Ducks 'n EGGs was created by using one of the images from the EGGsly io / L'EGGacy2 collections. This collection is minted on manifold and saved to arweave on the ethereum blockchain.

I'll be exploring many of the options manifold offers such as; editions, 1/1s,  open editions, burn, waitlist etc to name a few.

The EGGs images have been with me for at least 14 years now, their history dates back to several accidents, falls, concussions, and hitting my head... my EGG. The images explore the importance of balance, thinking, introspection and more. Please join me in the many facets of discovery and recovery.



x x x x x


Ross's distinctive, metaphorical, whimsical narrative, thought-provoking, abstract pieces revolve around the central theme of energy. She believes that the potential to create one's own energy has the power to alter a person's experiences & life circumstances. 

I don't know how long the following links will survive after me but you can also do an internet search for my name. 
With light, love, and gratitude. As of this date 01/25/23 I am 73yrs old.
